{
  "stem": "7683.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was constantly looking, maybe a bigger card shop, a gift store and thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then it once came up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Our daughter was married to somebody, which was a manager in a jewelry store in Old Saybrook.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this store was for sale.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had a buyer for my greeting card gift store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we sold that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I figured, he knows the jewelry business, and we can financially help it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we bought the business, and we took him as a partner, an equal partner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we bought this jewelry business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we moved to Branford, because it was so far away to travel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's the reason we ended up-- we wanted to be-- we didn't move to Saybrook because we wanted to be next to a bigger city.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because when we lived in Westport, we went often to New York.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we figured New Haven is a bigger city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the reason we moved here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there is--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My daughter-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My son-- my daughter, she is in New Haven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From her.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And our son is in-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] in Northborough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you break it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my message will be to be more open to people and not be hatred, understanding each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the distinction between people is not big.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is people make more out of by themselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if you don't hate, you're not a bigot, and you're open to hear what the other says, you find out they're just the same as everybody else, whether it's Jews or not Jews or black or whatever.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I think that is our message, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so because you learn only from the history, from the past.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
